Name: The Rack - Pool Billiard
About the game: The Rack is the world's most innovative social hub to play 8-Ball/9-Ball in virtual reality. With the realistic ball and table physics, you can put your real-life skills to the test! Whether you're an aspiring VR Pool professional or seek a more casual lifestyle, there is sure to be enough to keep you busy! Consider yourself a pool shark? Why not participate in one of the many tournaments, and take home the title! Or perhaps you are more of a collector, earn coins, to build your arsenal of cues and cosmetic accessories. !!! FREE 7 DAY TRIAL !!!
